    <p>Once you have a prescription, filling it is straightforward. Visit any Italian farmacia with your prescription and ID. Present your ricetta rossa or ricetta bianca and let the pharmacist know you need to fill the prescription. For electronic prescriptions, provide your prescription number and ID; pharmacists will retrieve your prescription from the national system.</p>
