    <p>Ricetta bianca prescriptions come from any licensed Italian physician, including private doctors, or from established farmacia relationships. Private doctors commonly issue ricetta bianca for patients without SSN coverage. Some pharmacists issue ricetta bianca refills for established patients requesting additional supplies of previously prescribed medications.</p>
