    <p>When searching for dentists, look for indicators of quality: professional qualifications displayed in office, modern equipment, appointment availability, and English-speaking staff. Many urban dentists speak English, particularly in major cities and tourist areas. Rural or smaller town dentists may have limited English—having an Italian-speaking friend help with initial contacts assists when language barriers exist.</p>
