    <p>Niacinamide-based products like Olay Regenerist or Eucerin DermoPure are effective for oily, acne-prone skin and cost €12-18. Niacinamide reduces sebum production and minimizes pores without the dryness of traditional acne treatments. Many expats find niacinamide products gentler than benzoyl peroxide while still effectively managing oily skin and breakouts.</p>

