    <p>Face sunscreens specifically formulated to not leave white residue or feel greasy are increasingly available. Lightweight formulations that work under makeup cost €15-22 and are particularly popular among expat women in Italy. Daily use of appropriate sunscreen is the single most important anti-aging skincare step, according to Italian dermatologists.</p>

