    <p>Omega-3 supplements have strong scientific evidence supporting benefits for cardiovascular health, blood pressure, triglycerides, and cognitive function. Quality fish oil supplements in Italy are pure and stable, without concerning heavy metal contamination that plagued some international brands. Dosing typically ranges from 1000-3000 mg EPA+DHA daily, with higher doses requiring medical supervision when taking blood thinners.</p>

